---- RUNTIME_PROFILE
# Verify Final filter table:
#  ID  Src. Node  Tgt. Node(s)  Eff. Tgt. Node(s)     Target type  ...
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
#   8          7             1                  1          REMOTE  ...
#   4          8             2                  N          REMOTE  ...
#   2          9          2, 3               2, 3  REMOTE, REMOTE  ...
#   0         10             4                  4          REMOTE  ...
#  10          6             0                  0           LOCAL  ...
#   5          8             0                  0           LOCAL  ...
row_regex: 8\s+7\s+1\s+1\s+REMOTE
row_regex: 4\s+8\s+2\s+N\s+REMOTE
row_regex: 2\s+9\s+2,\ 3\s+2,\ 3\s+REMOTE,\s*REMOTE
row_regex: 0\s+10\s+4\s+4\s+REMOTE
row_regex: 10\s+6\s+0\s+0\s+LOCAL
row_regex: 5\s+8\s+0\s+0\s+LOCAL
---- CALCITE_PLANNER_RUNTIME_PROFILE
# Verify Final filter table:
